  Local Dream is an Android app that runs Stable Diffusion locally on-device
  using Snapdragon NPU, CPU, and GPU. This project communicates with its local
  HTTP API (port 8081) but does not include, modify, or redistribute any part
  of the Local Dream source code or binaries.

Automask uses the HuggingFace Inference API with the model:
